title: Pet Friendly, Playground, Pet Stations
posting_body: ['Nestled on 42 beautiful acres, The Preston Apartments in McDonough, GA offers a unique combination of rural beauty and urban convenience in a luxurious community perfectly located in the Atlanta Suburbs.', 'Smartly designed interiors, outstanding resident service, and resort-style amenities make The Preston is the perfect choice to call home.', 'Property Amenities:', 'Pet Friendly', 'Playground', 'Car Care Center', 'GOFit Fitness Center', 'GOChat Business Center', 'Tennis Court', 'Pet Stations', 'Free Wellness Classes', '24 Hour Maintenance', 'Gated Community', '2 Swimming Pools', 'Online Resident Portal', 'Call Us Today!', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of your exact home.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!', 'Professionally managed by GoldOller Real Estate Investments, a provider of Fair Housing and Equal Opportunity.']
